Write a java program using ArrayList to display the following output:

LinkedList: [Java, Python, JavaScript, Java]
Updated LinkedList: [Java, Python, JavaScript, Kotlin]
import java.util.*;//code here
public class collection
{
    public static void main(String args[])
    {
        LinkedList<String> a=new LinkedList<String>();
        a.add("Java");
        a.add("Python");
        a.add("JavaScript");
        a.add("Java");
        System.out.println("Linkedlist: "+a);
        a.set(3,"Kotlin");
        System.out.println("Updated LinkedList: "+a);
    }
}
